            <title>[PIG-3940] NullPointerException writing .pig_header for field with null name (in JsonMetadata.java)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3940</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Pig throws an NPE writing .pig_header for field with null name. Attached patch has it instead write field name as &apos;$i&apos; corresponding to the field&apos;s zero-based position &amp;#8211; i.e., if the second field is unnamed, its header will be written as $1.&lt;/p&gt;

